Overview:
  Welcome to Task-2 of the EvolveIntern Internship!
  This task is designed to designing email templates with a focus on UI/UX involves
  creating visually appealing and user-friendly layouts that effectively communicate the message and engage recipients.

Task Details:

  Objective:
    Designing email templates with a focus on UI/UX involves creating visually appealing
    and user-friendly layouts that effectively communicate the message and engage recipients.

  Requirements:
    Here are the key considerations and steps for designing email templates:
      - [x]  Define the Objective.
      - [x]  Responsive Design.
      - [x]  Branding and Visual Identity.
      - [x]  Clear Call-to-Action (CTA).
      - [x]  Engaging Content Layout.
      - [x]  Visual Elements and Imagery.
      - [x]  Consistent Typography.
      - [x]  Personalization and Dynamic Content
      - [x]  Readability and Accessibility
      - [x]  Testing and Optimization
      - [x]  Compliance and Deliverability

  Research:
    This email template follows the outlined key considerations for a well-designed email,
    ensuring a user-friendly and visually appealing layout that effectively conveys the event's message and engages the recipient.

